VMS Strategic Land Trust declared aninitial dividend of 30 cts a share payable May 15 toshareholders of record April 20.    The dividend represents a 12 pct annual return based on thecompany's original offering price in December of 10 dlrs ashare. The return is guaranteed through December 31, 1988, thecompany said.    The trust invests in short term junior preconstructionmortgage loans and has total principal amount of investments ofapproximately 105.7 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;